### Hadith 3:797

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

Allah's Apostle said, "What a good Maniha (the she-camel which has
recently given birth and which gives profuse milk) is, and (what a good
Maniha) (the sheep which gives profuse milk, a bowl in the morning and
another in the evening) is!"

